1. This is the picture I like. (This is the picture which I like.)
2. She always read books I advised her. (She always read books which I advised her.3. Tom came to Minsk the day I left. (Tom came to Minsk the day when I left.)
4. I remember the day I went to school. (I remember the day when I went to
school.)
5. This is all he wanted to see. (This is all that he wanted to see.)
6. My daughter doesn't want to live with a man she doesn't love. (My daughter
doesn't want to live with a man who she doesn't love.)
